# 🌐 OFFLINE & ONLINE EXECUTION - COMPLETE GUIDE

## ✅ ALL 100+ Programming Languages Run OFFLINE and ONLINE!

The Angeh Reality Fabric now supports **complete offline execution** for all programming languages with automatic online/offline switching.

---

## 🎯 Key Features

### 1. **Offline-First Architecture**
- ✅ All code executes locally without internet
- ✅ Automatic caching of execution results  
- ✅ Local package management
- ✅ Model inference runs completely offline

### 2. **Online Enhancement**
- ✅ Cloud acceleration when available
- ✅ Automatic fallback to offline
- ✅ Package downloading and caching
- ✅ Model synchronization

### 3. **Auto Mode**
- ✅ Detects network availability
- ✅ Uses online when available
- ✅ Seamlessly falls back to offline
- ✅ No code changes required

---

