## 🎯 Use Cases

### 1. Air-Gapped Systems
```python
# No internet connection needed
runtime = OfflineRuntime(mode=ExecutionMode.OFFLINE)
runtime.execute('python', code)  # Works perfectly!
```

### 2. Mobile/Edge Devices
```python
# Works on phones, IoT, embedded
runtime = OfflineRuntime(mode=ExecutionMode.AUTO)
runtime.execute('python', code)  # Auto-adjusts to device
```

### 3. Development Environments
```python
# Fast local execution for testing
runtime = OfflineRuntime(mode=ExecutionMode.OFFLINE)
for test in tests:
    runtime.execute('python', test)  # Lightning fast!
```

### 4. Cloud with Fallback
```python
# Try cloud, fallback to local
runtime = OfflineRuntime(mode=ExecutionMode.ONLINE)
runtime.execute('python', code)  # Uses best option
```

