## 🔒 Security Benefits

### Offline Execution Advantages
1. **No Data Leakage** - Code never leaves your machine
2. **Privacy** - Sensitive code stays local
3. **Reliability** - Works without internet
4. **Speed** - No network latency
5. **Control** - Full execution control

